chliche und literarische Zeugnisse vom 8. bis ins 16. Jahrhundert.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aMultilingualismzGermanyxHistoryyTo 1500. 4aMehrsprachigkeit. 4aMittelalter / Literatur. 4aMittelalter / Sprache. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / General.2bisacsh  aMiddle Ages/Language.  aMiddle Ages/Literature.  aMultilingualism.1 aBALDZUHN, MICHAEL, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBOK, VACLAV, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBaldzuhn, Michael, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aDREWELOWSKY, ANDRÉ, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEhlen, Thomas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGRUBMÜLLER, KLAUS, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHAAG, GUNTRAM, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHAUBRICHS, WOLFGANG, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHunt, Tony, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMEINEKE, ECKHARD, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPUTZO, CHRISTINE, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPutzo, Christine, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aREDZICH, CAROLA, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWIELAND, GERNOT RUDOLF, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Literary and Cultural Studies 2000 - 2014z9783110637854oZDB-23-GLC08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2011z9783110261189oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyte